  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study examines and illustrates the utility of utilizing actigraphic measurements to
      assess treatment response.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Actigraphic measurements, repeated verbal fluency and multi-symptom operationally defined
      observations will be recorded for an 11 to 12 day baseline period and continued following
      neurosurgical tumor resection until a repeat MRI is completed three months after the
      procedure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
